item.title: About
item.description: About Me Yueming Yang Shandong University|SDU · School of Energy and Power Engineering Master Degree Candidate Research Interest Yueming Yang research interests are the computational fluid dynamics; the design, simulation, and optimization of supercritical CO2 (SCO2) radial inflow turbines and centrifugal compressors; physical properties of working fluids in SCO2 power cycles; and modeling of fluid- and thermo- dynamic systems (mainly the SCO2 Brayton cycles). Education 2016.9 – 2020.6 Bachelor’s Degree in Engineering

item.title: Life
item.description: Interest In addition to carefully studying the curriculum, I also had a strong interest in computational fluid dynamics. I have been able to spot some phenomena and solve some engineering problems with this tool. Hobby In my spare time, I often take part in various football matches. This sport keeps me energetic and motivated.
